  "text": "DNA was extracted from blood spots with Instagene ® Matrix resin (BioRad © , Marnes la Coquette, France), according to the manufacturer's instructions. Parasite species were confirmed by real-time PCR, using species-specific primers previously described by de Monbrison [CITATION_1] , with a protocol adapted for the RotorGene ® 3000 thermocycler (Corbett Life Science ® , Sydney, Australia).",
